latestIgtvVideos.title: My experience with @goldsgymindia
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
As a person who would work out at the gym almost every day, I was waiting for the day gyms would open after the pandemic lockdown.

Of course, I wanted to ensure my gym is safe and following all safety protocols! Today I'm at my favourite workout location @goldsgymindia Bandra West.

Happy to see that Gold’s Gym is a safe place to workout and the safety of the members is their #1 priority!

They are celebrating their 18th Anniversary in India!

If you still cannot make it to the gym, Gold's Gym India is offering various digital fitness programs.

Visit their website or download the Gold’s Gym India app to restart your fitness goals!

🎥 @sqlain_shaikh 
#GoldsGymIndia #GoldsGymIndiaApp #MakingIndiaFit #StrongerTogether
